('Lagasca', 'Mental Health', 'English-speaking psychology and therapy center in Madrid Centro, approved by the Comunidad de Madrid. Team of recognized psychologists and therapists specializing in therapeutic accompaniment using an integrative, humanistic approach. Specializes in helping English-speaking emigrants navigate cultural adaptation, distance, uprooting, and loss of reference points. Services include individual psychotherapy, couples therapy, family mediation, play therapy for children, psychological guidance, and online therapy sessions. All therapists are experienced in working with international clients and understand the unique challenges faced by expats living abroad.', 'C/ Villanueva 27, 1º Dch., 28001 Madrid', 'Madrid', 'Madrid', '+34 91 319 4348', 'info@lagasca.es', 'https://lagasca.es/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
